Notebook[{
Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"(*", "\"\< \n\nThis notebook contains general definitions and \
numerical routines\nfor worldline-instanton calculations in QED and gravity. \
\n\nAuthor: Greger Torgrimsson\n\nMuch of this code was developed for:\
\[IndentingNewLine]\nP. Semren and G.~Torgrimsson,\n``Worldline instantons \
for nonperturbative particle production by space and time dependent \
gravitational fields''\nPhys. Rev. D \
\!\(\*StyleBox[\"113\",FontWeight->\"Bold\"]\), 056005 (2026)  \
\[IndentingNewLine]\nand\[IndentingNewLine]\n``Scattered wave functions and \
worldline instantons for particle production in curved spacetime'' \n(to \
appear)\n\nMost of the underlying methods were developed in: \
\[IndentingNewLine]\nG. Degli Esposti and G. Torgrimsson,\n``Worldline \
instantons for the momentum spectrum of Schwinger pair production in \
spacetime dependent fields''\nPhys. Rev. D \
\!\(\*StyleBox[\"107\",FontWeight->\"Bold\"]\), 056019 (2023)\
\[IndentingNewLine]\nG. Degli Esposti and G. Torgrimsson,\n``Momentum \
spectrum of Schwinger pair production in four-dimensional e-dipole fields''\n\
Phys. Rev. D \!\(\*StyleBox[\"109\",FontWeight->\"Bold\"]\), 016013 (2024)\
\[IndentingNewLine]\nG. Degli Esposti and G. Torgrimsson,\n``Momentum \
spectrum of nonlinear Breit-Wheeler pair production in spacetime fields''\n\
Phys. Rev. D \!\(\*StyleBox[\"110\",FontWeight->\"Bold\"]\), 076017 (2024)\
\[IndentingNewLine]\nG. Degli Esposti and G. Torgrimsson,\n``Schwinger pair \
production in spacetime fields: Moir{\\'e} patterns, Aharonov-Bohm phases, \
and Sturm-Liouville eigenvalues''\nPhys. Rev. D \
\!\(\*StyleBox[\"112\",FontWeight->\"Bold\"]\), 016026 (2025)\n\n\>\"", 
  "*)"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9910424425763874`*^9, 3.991042444894575*^9}, {
  3.991045833326086*^9, 
  3.991045929792948*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a24535f5-81b3-f242-8455-\
070e620164c6"],

